82
00:03:46,351 --> 00:03:47,560
{\an8}I got 'em from Disco Janet.

83
00:03:47,644 --> 00:03:48,478
{\an8}Thanks, Disco Janet!

84
00:03:48,561 --> 00:03:49,395
