just because I stole a hot dog.

92
00:04:04,535 --> 00:04:06,079
{\an8}Well, a hot dog-shaped car.

93
00:04:06,162 --> 00:04:07,580
{\an8}I stole the Wienermobile.

94
00:04:07,664 --> 00:04:09,582
